{"tw": {"2962420": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "外送熱", "steam_appid": 2962420, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962420/extras/6ab710dc6da49d2d19c1951f7051d7ee.avif?t=1742551526\" width=616 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962420/extras/f8b00438d204e40b878d54cfff29d511.avif?t=1742551526\" width=616 height=414 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆故事：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身為一位敬業的外送師，在一次工作中邂逅了清純可愛的女大生—奈緒</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著送餐次數的增加，你與奈緒的感情也日漸升溫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同時因為工作的關係，也邂逅了許多其他女性</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >趕快跳上你的外送腳踏車， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一步一步踏出你的後宮生活吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962420/extras/bca77e8ac6ea3f23a3667f85a3cf16de.avif?t=1742551526\" width=616 height=262 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆角色介紹</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962420/extras/a038bfbc8347ad4f6a0b01d619d35bbe.avif?t=1742551526\" width=616 height=300 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962420/extras/34d8f3d08d1c62ebece7818bdbb4b33b.avif?t=1742551526\" width=616 height=300 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962420/extras/77745a053959f8320762f34bd218c81a.avif?t=1742551526\" width=616 height=300 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962420/extras/f1424889c8e684e4eb36a891a34dc53a.avif?t=1742551526\" width=616 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆玩法：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作為外送模擬戀愛養成經營遊戲，玩家將有4位女角可以攻略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家除了每天要外送賺錢之外，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >還需要滿足女角們的各種需求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當然，也包含了生理需求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲中將會有特殊道具加強主角各項數值，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >讓玩家可以成為｢最強外送員｣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了日常送餐外，遊戲中也有夾娃娃機台、調酒製作、甜點製作等輕鬆簡單的小遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962420/extras/dd99a1c7f62baa318156df72c03521a5.poster.avif?t=1742551526\" width=324 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962420/extras/dd99a1c7f62baa318156df72c03521a5.webm?t=1742551526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962420/extras/dd99a1c7f62baa318156df72c03521a5.mp4?t=1742551526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962420/extras/2b28b7da8170521614a3bedc68c10f70.poster.avif?t=1742551526\" width=400 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962420/extras/2b28b7da8170521614a3bedc68c10f70.webm?t=1742551526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2962420/extras/2b28b7da8170521614a3bedc68c10f70.mp4?t=1742551526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇每位女角皆有4種不同體位可選擇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇H場景紙娃娃系統，隨心所欲更換服裝</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇20張以上的CG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇全